Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.33,0:19:05.10,In2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}The place changes and goes. Like a wind, like clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.25,0:19:18.90,In2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Like the traces of the heart, no halt at the places.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.90,0:19:30.40,In2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}The place is so far away, be far apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.40,0:19:43.45,In2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}People's hand does not reach, so merely has the worship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.26,0:19:55.75,In2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}The place is a lofty lord, can't meet nobody put on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.31,0:20:08.69,In2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}We will lose the place, so lofty which changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.72,0:20:20.64,In2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Not all were desired. However, we're never sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.33,0:19:05.10,in2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}那里不断变换  如风  又似云
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.25,0:19:18.90,in2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}好似心底的涟漪  不会停留一处
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.90,0:19:30.40,in2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}那里如此遥远  远离我们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.40,0:19:43.45,in2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}远在伸手难及之处  只有虔诚信奉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.26,0:19:55.75,in2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}那里就如崇高的神明  难以企及
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.31,0:20:08.69,in2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}终将失去  变得遥不可及的那里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.72,0:20:20.64,in2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}这一切并非所愿  但我们从不悲伤…


